  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4919394">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4919394/" class="title-link">撷芳主人 2011/04/23 说</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4919394"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamAngelica/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36739542-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamAngelica/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">貳歸</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-23"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-23 20:37:07</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4919394_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  稿费的扣税实在有点重了，这本《Q版》仅算重绘的这13个月，稿费平均下来每个月只有2100，最后扣税都扣了3500……作为无业人员，再投入全部精力去画这样的书已经不行了，哪能每个月都让家里供着，看来家人说的是对的，这不是生存之道……   

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4919394/#comments">(30回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">43有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
