  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4713016">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4713016/" class="title-link">很适合收藏的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4713016"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/iwowo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37600497-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iwowo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">艾窝窝</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-28"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-28 15:00:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4713016_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         厚厚的一本书包含了作者数年的心血。每一位看到了这本书的朋友都对里面精美的插图表示出浓浓的兴趣。而文字部分也更是作者花费心力去研究搜集的。     能够有这样一位既了解明代服饰文化，又能亲自绘制出图画的作者为我们呈现出这样一本书，我觉得实在是件极其难能可贵...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4713016/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4713016_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4713016_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



